  &= \frac{1/7}{1-1/7} + \frac{1/49}{1-1/49} \\
  &= \frac{1/7}{6/7} + \frac{1/49}{48/49} \\
  &= \frac{1}{6} + \frac{1}{48} \\
  &= \boxed{ \frac{3}{16} }
